      <title>据称宁德时代供应商Lopal将寻求2亿美元收购印度尼西亚子公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/catl-supplier-lopal-said-to-seek-200-million-for-indonesia-unit</link>
